com.kontakt.sdk.android.common.model

Interface IBeacon

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Beacon

    public interface IBeacon
    Beacon model represents JSON model of Beacon device with kontakt.io logic applied. Beacon is a property of a Manager (IManager). It acts also as a container for Actions and may be assigned to certain Venue (IVenue).
